General Information

Soothing age-defying eye treatment

Warnings

Test patch is recommended for first use. Discontinue if irritation occurs

Ingredients

Royal Nectar Bee Venom Eye Cream ingredients are Distilled Water, Sweet Almond Oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glycerin, Coco-Caprylate, Shea Butter, Nectar Ease (Manuka Honey with Bee Venom), Avocado Oil, Apricot Kernel Oil, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Cetearyl Alcohol, Parfum, Chamomile Flower Oil, Vitamine E, Green Tea Leaf Extract, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Easyliance, Dehydroacetic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol.

Directions

Apply to cleansed face. Gently dot the cream around your eye area. Massage into the skin
